}

As Employee, you can request the creation of a category :  
category will have status of PENDING  
RequestBody example :  
{  
"name" :"Cats and Dogs"  
}

As an admin can update any category, given the id and the new name of the category.  
Body request :  
{ 

"id": 41 ,  
 "name": "flowers"

}

As an Employee can update any category, given the id and the new name of the category.  
Body request :  
